content:
Improve environment, social, and governance (ESG) report accuracy by using Einstein generative AI to compare the guidance for a question with your proposed response, directly in Microsoft 365 Word with the Salesforce Disclosure and Compliance Hub for Microsoft 365 Word add-in.

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions with the Net Zero Cloud Growth license and the Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Service, or Einstein for Platform add-on license.

Einstein generative AI is available in Lightning Experience. To purchase the Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Service, or Einstein Platform add-on, contact your Salesforce account executive.

To edit Word documents, you need a Microsoft 365 license.

These improvements help refine the quality of the disclosure reports by seeking specific guidance for each question, analyzing the response to a question by using Einstein, and providing explanations for each question and related question and the expected response.
title: Improving ESG Report Accuracy with Einstein Generative AI
